 2013-06042013-05-30AAFC,  GRAIN COMM,  ,  ,  ,  ,  , 
ActCanada Grain Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Canada Grain Regulations
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE CANADA GRAIN REGULATIONS in order to (1) establish new user fees which reflect the current role of the Canadian Grain Commission; (2) update existing fee amounts and provide for an annual adjustment of fees reflective of inflation; and (3) consolidate various existing user fees and establish a five year fee schedule.
